cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY

The paper proposes a method that combines reinforcement learning and imitation learning from observation to perform imitation using a single expert demonstration. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper specifically focuses on robot control tasks and robot soccer tasks, which further supports the likelihood of these sub-categories.
